{"tid":1684210,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"整合左近期被捕既勇武condom","createTime":"2019-10-31T03:37:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-01T14:13:28.000Z","uid":240250,"like":11,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"5601e22d3da70fe872b746ad4f1a8cbc126b1377","tid":1684210,"uid":240250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T03:37:02.000Z","msg":"對不起，我被捕了<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1669632\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1669632</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n我係被捕人士即將上庭，有一個心願，想大家幫我做。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1672793\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1672793</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n我今年中六 等緊上庭<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1678699\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1678699</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n各位手足，《香城online》我要quit game了<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1681171\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1681171</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另一邊廂又睇下班冷氣軍師仲緊乜，原來仲縮係冷氣房度內鬥緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最新風向 逼你做死士 最激 唔做就係垃圾<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1683889\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1683889</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n勇武派，你付出左自己既前途，甚至人生，爭取到d咩？多謝同對唔住邊個唔識講？上面幾位被捕人士，除左喺連登得到一大堆廉價既感謝同道歉之外仲得到d咩？<br />\n當畀你最後贏左，就可以當冇事發生？會唔會太天真？其實五大訴求之中，大部分人都只係期望爭取到三項，因為大家心底裡都知道撤銷抗爭者控罪同真普選係冇可能既事。<br />\n<br />\n被捕人士最後好大機會要留案底，以後大公司同政府工冇你地份，你想要前途冇，想要舒服又冇，你一世都只能夠用勞力同汗水換取微薄既金錢，做低下階層辛苦工，仲想諗拍拖、結婚、生仔女？而嗰班唯恐天下不亂既冷氣軍師，喺你地贏左就出黎攞彩，輸左就唔出聲，永遠立於不敗之地，食完花生之後就狗衝大公司同政府工，繼續涼冷氣un un腳，留低一句廉價既「多謝」就由得你自生自滅。<br />\n<br />\n畀個實際少少既建議你地，未被捕既即刻收手，乜柒活動都唔好再出，被捕既就搵返門手藝學下，係就係預左一世做辛苦工架喇，但起碼叫有d錢先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c622b2c199497b5777fd149de47671fba68704a3","tid":1684210,"uid":55973,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T03:37:55.000Z","msg":"改左名喎"},{"pid":"9c06dcd7ec8b4c7d10f47e85aacc220f4f04c8d5","tid":1684210,"uid":244876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T03:38:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />樹窿再次歡迎大家加入<br />\n知道過去兩個月，大家既生活都過得好壓抑。有人係依兩個月之間同父母嗌大交，同伴侶分手，同朋友斷交，有人晚晚夜歸，有人用到無哂錢。或者你覺得好迷惘好無奈，或者你覺得無岀路。有見及此，開左個谷俾大家入黎吐下苦水，只談現實，不談夢境。希望大家可以舒發下，減減壓，然後大家一齊繼續向前行。<br />\n<br />\n發緊想發未發就發夢都唔好係公海講<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n保障大家安全<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n講明先 係歡迎任何人講既<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n理得你藍定黃 狗定人 貓定兔<br />\n我地好希望大家可以有個好始既渠道釋放咁耐以來既情緒<br />\n如果大家有朋友仔想入來都無任歡迎咖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同埋記得不指責不要質問 任何指責及質問均無助大家發洩情緒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nlink:<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/ourtreehole\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fourtreehole&d=N2LCmr%2FexNvWBpgyITFnA8WiAETkOtN%2FvKUl8N5Dwlc%3D&h=12edde84\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/ourtreehole</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n無論你係邊一到，保護自己，不要透露個人資料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港人，反抗！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aba575503d42c1f0062f3f38f414e6fb699bc259","tid":1684210,"uid":50386,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T03:39:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BycbwVS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBycbwVS.png&h=2c953acf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n又係叫人做自己唔撚做<br />\n拉"},{"pid":"080da3ce78b13a29a0146f7614c8f669c5a81f7b","tid":1684210,"uid":51701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T03:40:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qJL8y9G.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqJL8y9G.jpg&h=a95a5261&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"213eae138241629f747c9e03365afecf65e71b75","tid":1684210,"uid":205162,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T03:45:58.000Z","msg":"大家小心佢"},{"pid":"0d2e39da477aee51e65f962bf8091698e39c6b76","tid":1684210,"uid":162046,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T03:46:27.000Z","msg":"拉<br />\nGood morning sir"},{"pid":"0a53958f81b6c38c125c7270a47167e27f995d27","tid":1684210,"uid":240250,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c622b2c199497b5777fd149de47671fba68704a3","tid":1684210,"uid":55973,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T03:37:55.000Z","msg":"改左名喎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T03:52:56.000Z","msg":"我叫徐永強，花名Fu gor，行不改名坐不改姓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bb5940f508fa81b8adc50b1935e6ded74ce6c85","tid":1684210,"uid":55010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T04:03:39.000Z","msg":"咁撚似啲狗講既，唔緊要人權法括免左<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b81e4dc6b4a5bf274d8aeeb5ec30f0f12a9d2e7","tid":1684210,"uid":256056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T04:04:37.000Z","msg":"有人唔做 你做狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0c558f412a21533c3c64c6386fedb34469b2dcf","tid":1684210,"uid":52773,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T04:08:07.000Z","msg":"一向都當condom<br />\n背後的都笑佢哋on9"},{"pid":"cb0bd3ce1615c61c2105d618fefd1d763d954e60","tid":1684210,"uid":279356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T04:09:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/04EdLjM.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F04EdLjM.gif&h=e7e4e8ef&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2c7c1f7300d2972fd346af11cbb1f778a324799d","tid":1684210,"uid":240250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f0c558f412a